---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Chouhan Industries | Open Hardware"
  ogTitle="About | Chouhan Industries"
  description="Founded on the conviction that the best hardware should be free for anyone to study, build upon, and improve."
  url="https://chouhan.ai/about.html"
>

  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p class="page-sub">Founded on the conviction that the best hardware should be free for anyone to study, build
        upon, and improve.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="about-body">
        <div class="lead">
          Precision hardware, designed for the public and published in full: schematics, tolerances, and processes,
          without restriction.
        </div>
        <div class="detail">
          <p>The manufacturing industry has long operated on opacity. Proprietary designs, closed tolerances,
            undisclosed processes. We believe this model is not only unnecessary. It is actively harmful to the pace
            of human progress.</p>
          <p>We started Chouhan Industries to demonstrate that premium quality and full transparency are not in
            conflict. That you can build things that last, share everything about how you built them, and still
            maintain the highest standard.</p>
          <p>Everything we make is licensed under CERN OHL-S v2.0. This is not a marketing position. It is a legal
            commitment that the work stays open, permanently.</p>
          <p>The direction is consumer hardware you <em>truly own</em>: fully open, <em>customizable</em> down to the
            source, and yours to build from the files, adapt to your needs, or simply buy finished.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section surface">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="section-label">Team</p>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card">
          <p class="name">Animesh Chouhan</p>
          <p class="role">Founder</p>
          <p>Engineer and open-source advocate. Building hardware that belongs to everyone.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 16px; display: flex; gap: 16px;">
            <a href="https://x.com/animeshsingh338" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
              style="font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--subtle);">X</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/animesh-chouhan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
              style="font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--subtle);">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="https://animeshchouhan.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
              style="font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--subtle);">Website</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <p class="name" style="color: var(--subtle);">Open Position</p>
          <p class="role">Hardware Engineer</p>
          <p>We are looking for engineers who believe the best work is done in public. <a href="contact.html"
              style="color: var(--gold);">Get in touch.</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <p class="name" style="color: var(--subtle);">Open Position</p>
          <p class="role">Manufacturing Lead</p>
          <p>Production experience with a commitment to quality and documentation. <a href="contact.html"
              style="color: var(--gold);">Get in touch.</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
